      "text": "Fig. 1 shows a general model for how an application (1), with an integrated OPC client (2), can connect to a PLC (8). There are three different communication parts in this model: the OPC interface (3), i.e., COM/DCOM, the communication interface (5) between the OPC server (4) and the gateway (6), and the gateway interface (7) to the PLC."
